title: Bug 120315: Display property not taking effect in new PDF emitter
OB: When the display property of an item is set to "none", it does not hide the item in the new PDF emitter.
SR:
To reproduce the issue: 
1. Open the application and navigate to the PDF emitter feature. 
2. Create a new document or open an existing document. 
3. Set the display property of an item to "none". 
4. Generate the PDF using the new emitter. 
5. Observe that the item is still visible in the generated PDF despite the display property being set to "none".
